TaHdxeHF3eWpPLUtGdFpzIiwiemlkIjo\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"326! idWFh\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"327  IiwiZ3JhbnRfdHlwZSI6InVybjppZXRmOnBhcmFtczpvYXV0aDpncmFudC10eXBlOmp3dC1iZWFyZXIiLCJ1c2VyX2lkIjoiZDExNDg0YmQtMWExNC00MmNiLThlNzk\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"327! tZmYz\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"328  YjhiMTAzODM0IiwiYXpwIjoic2FzLmxhdW5jaGVyIiwic2NvcGUiOlsidWFhLnVzZXIiXSwiZXhwIjoxNzI4MDMzNzU1LCJpYXQiOjE3MjgwMzAxNTUsImp0aSI6IjY\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"12                                                         The SAS System                       Friday, October  4, 2024 01:06:00 PM\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"title\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"title\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"328! yMGI3\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"329  ODVhZGQwODRlOGY4ODdjNGI2MjE0NDUxYTg3IiwiZW1haWwiOiJNYXR0aWEuR3VnbGllbG1lbGxpQHNhcy5jb20iLCJyZXZfc2lnIjoiNTY0MzY2YTkiLCJjaWQiOiJ\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"329! zYXMu\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"330  bGF1bmNoZXIifQ.sZ9qK1KJDaM16-KMvS1R14EwRdRorDNQhVax0GK7-IWXXwF25M8hLSJhzl6FOiHIypwcnbf9LH_OqGCZEDcNakfFq6e0W5sjfS7KyppqVjBndOuv\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"330! 1YqOa\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"331  jhHrTe879hIHvIFJSK0dmkrSr5aIBGSmVxu1bPzkGMM0gdkY5VuT1zT_Qje9vk0ZFlXbt-hxqebAKgxyqjGZWOTAan7eDecqG7k10Z6aYj_UVqb-TLM_uoQ1NM3FE30\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"331! LWnPk\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"332  HwKMRQs8VPV8MfKWbh1tdT66f_Lw-_K2cELXnMcKJFE1OlRioVMAznUBY05M6pdQPvLTiOG7m_HD_LeH5G-mRw3lBUfrg\\\"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"333  %mend;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"334  ;*';*\\\";*/;run;quit;ods html5(id=vscode) close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t}\n]","mime":"application/vnd.sas.compute.log.lines"}]}]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"We are now ready to use the `REGISTERMODEL` procedure to register the model in SAS Model Manager.\n`PROC REGISTERMODEL` Statement Options:\n- `NAME` (required). It specifies the name to register the model under in SAS Model Manager.\n- `OAUTHTOKEN` (required). It specifies the name of the authentication token for connecting to SAS Model Manager.\n- `SERVER` (required). It specifies the root URL for your SAS Viya server where SAS Model Manager is located.\n- ALGORITHM (optional). It specifies the algorithm that was used to train the model.\n- DATA (optional). It names the input data table for PROC REGISTERMODEL to use. The default is the most recently created data table.\n- DESCRIPTION (optional). It specifies the description of the model.\n- FUNCTION (optional). It specifies the model function type.\n- REPLACE (optional). It specifies that you want to replace an existing model with a new one if the new model would have the same model name in the same project.\n\nThe ASSESSMENT Statement enables you to assess the model and register assessment statistics in SAS Model Manager. To enable assessment:\n- the FUNCTION option value in the PROC REGISTERMODEL statement must be PREDICTION or CLASSIFICATION.\n- the TARGET statement must be specified.\n- the DATA option in the PROC REGISTERMODEL statement must be specified to provide the training data table.\n\nThe ASTOREMODEL Statement names an analytic store to be registered. You must specify the STORE option, which names the external file that contains the analytic store holding the model to be registered.\n\nThe PROJECT Statement specifies the project in which to register the model. In our case, we specify the name of the SAS Model Manager project to register the model in, and the folder name where the SAS Model Manager project resides.\n\nThe TARGET Statement names the variable whose values the model tries to predict. The following two options must be specified after typing the variable name:\n- LEVEL. It specifies the level of measurement of the target variable. In our case, the measurement level is binary.\n- EVENT. It must be specified if LEVEL=BINARY or NOMINAL. In these cases, it specifies the event level of the target.\n\nTo avoid SSL certificate issues, set the `SSLREQCERT=\"allow\"`, which allows to run PROC REGISTERMODEL even if no certificate is provided:","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"options set=SSLREQCERT=\"allow\";\n\nproc registermodel\n      name = \"Tree Astore\"\n      description = \"Decision Tree Astore Model\"\n      data = mylib.hmeq\n      algorithm = TREE\n      function = CLASSIFICATION\n      server = \"https://create.demo.sas.com\"\n      oauthtoken = \"myTokenName\"\n      replace;\n   project name=\"registermodel-project\" folder=\"myFolder\";\n   astoremodel store = \"/workspaces/myfolder/workbench-session/treeAstore.sasast\";\n   target bad / level=binary event=\"1\";\n   assessment;\nrun;","outputs":[{"items":[{"data":"[\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"335  /** LOG_START_INDICATOR **/\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"336  title;footnote;ods _all_ close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"337  ods graphics on;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"338  ods html5(id=vscode) style=HTMLEncore options(bitmap_mode='inline' svg_mode='inline');\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: Writing HTML5(VSCODE) Body file: sashtml17.htm\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"339  %let _SASPROGRAMFILE = %nrquote(%nrstr(/workspaces/myfolder/workbench-session/Model registration - SAS.sasnb));\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"340  options set=SSLREQCERT=\\\"allow\\\";\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"341  \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"342  proc registermodel\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"343        name = \\\"Tree Astore\\\"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"344        description = \\\"Decision Tree Astore Model\\\"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"345        data = mylib.hmeq\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"346        algorithm = TREE\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"347        function = CLASSIFICATION\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"348        server = \\\"https://create.demo.sas.com\\\"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"349        oauthtoken = \\\"myTokenName\\\"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"350        replace;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"351     project name=\\\"registermodel-project\\\" folder=\\\"myFolder\\\";\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"352     astoremodel store = \\\"/workspaces/myfolder/workbench-session/treeAstore.sasast\\\";\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"353     target bad / level=binary event=\\\"1\\\";\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"354     assessment;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"355  run;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"ERROR: An error occurred while querying the services URL https://create.demo.sas.com/modelRepository.\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"error\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: The SAS System stopped processing this step because of errors.\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: PROCEDURE REGISTERMODEL used (Total process time):\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      real time           0.39 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      cpu time            0.22 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"356  ;*';*\\\";*/;run;quit;ods html5(id=vscode) close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t}\n]","mime":"application/vnd.sas.compute.log.lines"}]}]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"**Note**. In order to connect to SAS Model Manager, your SAS Viya server where SAS Model Manager is located must have the IP address of your SAS Viya Workbench in its allowed IP ranges. If you need to change the allowed IP ranges, please contact your SAS administrator.","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"","outputs":[]}]